343
00:24:52,360 --> 00:24:52,840
Right.

344
00:24:52,840 --> 00:24:54,000
the strongest nail household.

345
00:25:04,960 --> 00:25:05,680
Linlu.

346
00:25:06,640 --> 00:25:07,480
