370
00:25:57,720 --> 00:25:59,640
Zhong Wan Zhen, do you have to say that?

371
00:26:00,880 --> 00:26:02,240
Stop arguing.

372
00:26:02,560 --> 00:26:05,800
Come on. Come on.

373
