506
00:35:15,280 --> 00:35:18,640
Maybe we'll shine around your seat.

507
00:35:19,640 --> 00:35:21,640
That sounds really good.

508
00:35:21,800 --> 00:35:22,920
If you go to the scene,

509
00:35:22,920 --> 00:35:24,640
