591
00:40:26,880 --> 00:40:28,640
No, thanks.

592
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:44,320
I remember.

593
00:40:44,320 --> 00:40:46,640
In high school, every Monday was our instant noodles day.

594
00:40:47,160 --> 00:40:49,640
We sat under the flag-rising platform to eat noodles.

595
00:40:50,640 --> 00:40:51,440
Really?

596
00:40:53,880 --> 00:40:55,840
We always eat golden soup and beef.

597
00:40:55,960 --> 00:40:57,320
Because it always gets one free.

598
00:40:57,720 --> 00:40:59,840
But my favorite is pork bone soup.

599
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,200
It's the odor of winter yin.

600
00:41:10,200 --> 00:41:11,920
It's the odor of winter yin.

601
00:41:15,240 --> 00:41:16,560
You remember everything.

602
00:41:22,120 --> 00:41:24,920
Can I ask what happened tonight?

603
00:41:33,000 --> 00:41:34,520
The dancers

